                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190915-6-defend125 t18190915-6-punish35"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 20.</p>

               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Best.</p>
